OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,FFour-time Paralympic gold-medallist
OL,7,Fand former Formula One driver Alex
OL,8,FZanardi has died at the age of 59, his
OL,9,Ffamily has said.
OL,11,FZanardi, from Bologna, Italy, made his
OL,12,FF1 debut in 1991, and competed for
OL,13,Ffive seasons, achieving a best finish
OL,14,Fof sixth at the 1993 Brazilian Grand
OL,15,FPrix.
OL,17,FBut his life changed dramatically when
OL,18,Fhe was involved in a major crash in
OL,19,F2001, which resulted in both of his
OL,20,Flegs being amputated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
