OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,FZanardi recovered from his life-
OL,7,Fchanging operation to become a
OL,8,FParalympic champion of para-cycling
OL,9,Fand one of Italy's most decorated
OL,10,FParalympians.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHe first competed in the London Games
OL,18,Fin 2012 and claimed two gold medals,
OL,19,Fbefore gaining another two in Rio de
OL,20,FJaneiro four years later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
