OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,FZanardi also won multiple times at the
OL,7,FUCI para-cycling Road World
OL,8,FChampionships and most recently in
OL,9,FEmmen in 2019.
OL,11,FIn 2020, he suffered another serious
OL,12,Faccident after being struck by a truck
OL,13,Fwhile competing in a charity para-
OL,14,Fcycling relay in Tuscany, causing him
OL,15,Fserious head injuries.
OL,17,FAfter more than a year of treatment,
OL,18,Fhe returned home, and his condition
OL,19,Fwas kept confidential until the news
OL,20,Fof his passing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
