OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,F"It is with deep sorrow that the
OL,7,Ffamily announces the passing of
OL,8,FAlessandro Zanardi, which occurred
OL,9,Fsuddenly yesterday evening, 1 May,"
OL,10,Fhis family said in a statement.
OL,12,F"Alex passed away peacefully,
OL,13,Fsurrounded by the love of his family
OL,14,Fand friends.
OL,16,F"The family would like to express
OL,17,Ftheir heartfelt thanks to all those
OL,18,Fwho are showing their support at this
OL,19,Ftime and asks that their grief and
OL,20,Fprivacy be respected during this
OL,21,Fperiod of mourning."
