CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,FMarco Giunio De Sanctis, president of
OL,7,Fthe Italian Paralympic Committee, said
OL,8,FZanardi was a champion and an athlete
OL,9,F"capable of rewriting history" in a
OL,10,Fstatement shared by the Olympic Games.
OL,12,F"Above all, he was the one who truly
OL,13,Flaunched the Paralympic Movement,
OL,14,Fmaking a decisive contribution to the
OL,15,Fspread of its culture, in Italy and
OL,16,Faround the world," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,F"He was a great communicator, a man
OL,7,Fcapable of connecting with everyone
OL,8,Fthrough his simplicity and strength.
OL,9,FHe could have held any role, because
OL,10,Fhe was an extraordinary champion in
OL,11,Fsport and in life. His immediacy, his
OL,12,Fauthenticity, and his humanity will
OL,13,Fremain an indelible legacy."
OL,15,FThe FIA, the global governing body of
OL,16,Fmotor sport, paid tribute to Zanardi
OL,17,Fin a social media post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
