OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777759862
OL,3,CFormer F1 driver and Paralympic
OL,4,Cchampion Alex Zanardi dies aged 59
OL,6,F"The FIA is saddened to learn of the
OL,7,Fpassing of Alex Zanardi, the former
OL,8,FFormula 1 driver, two-time CART
OL,9,Fchampion whose journey from life-
OL,10,Fchanging accident to Paralympics gold
OL,11,Fmedallist made him one of sport's most
OL,12,Fadmired competitors and an enduring
OL,13,Fsymbol of courage and determination,"
OL,14,Fit said.
